      "doc": "<p>Find the specified text in the provided image or grab a screenshot to search from. The region can be specified directly in the robot file using <span class=\"name\">RPA.core.geometry.to_region</span></p>\n<p>Args: text: text or regex to search for, use the format <span class=\"name\">regex:&lt;regex-string&gt;</span> if the text we want to find is a regex. region: region to search for the text. image: image to search from.</p>\n<p>Returns: The list of matched text regions where the text was found. Each match is a dictionary with \"text\", \"region\", and \"confidence\".</p>",
